{"Sid":0,"Did":124043,"Id":"512846","Title":"二結王公廟舊廟步口簷廊石柱","ImageUrl":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-07-22/b6e8a148-a5e6-4d76-82a3-34598e62c3ee/collection/5c9fac88-aab2-4c99-98e2-63005a7c0623/109-her-pa-2220-202007192227235f1457e39261d0.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-07-22/b6e8a148-a5e6-4d76-82a3-34598e62c3ee/collection/80b7334b-855b-4453-9f81-239a0e3043d3/109-her-pa-2220-202007192227235f1457e39261d1.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-07-22/b6e8a148-a5e6-4d76-82a3-34598e62c3ee/collection/0d11fd02-dfd2-4683-a42b-5a2d9a0753f6/109-her-pa-2220-202007192227235f1457e39261d2.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-07-22/b6e8a148-a5e6-4d76-82a3-34598e62c3ee/collection/11336e87-99ff-4589-ad78-7b5cc3ebfae9/109-her-pa-2220-202007192227235f1457e39261d3.jpg","IndexCode":"Culture_Place","CustomColumns":{"Description":"\n\n二結王公廟步口簷廊石柱，因配合中央明間凹壽作法，即利用顯露在外的柱身正面與面向凹壽一面施以雕刻裝飾。步口簷廊石柱正面以陰刻方式雕刻以廟名「鎮安」為首字之楹聯：「鎮蘭陽之二結靈傳漳浦」、「安朱祚於安坑志效桃園」，並以蝙蝠啣聯之方式呈現。龍邊楹聯邊框刻有「昭和己巳年冬月之日吉旦」，說明此對石柱為1929（昭和4）年製作敬獻。步口簷廊石柱面向凹壽中門側，則以淺浮雕的方式雕製「八仙」，故又稱「八仙柱」。龍邊柱由上而下分別雕以：雙手高舉蒲扇的漢鍾離、左手持魚鼓右手高舉的張果老、左手高舉拂塵背揹七星劍的呂洞賓，以及經常被臺灣傳統匠師替為八仙之一的劉海，可見其雙手持串錢誘惑下方喜愛金錢的三腳金蟾。虎邊柱由上而下之八仙為：腳拄拐杖手拿葫蘆的李鐵拐、右手高舉玉板左手撫鬚的曹國舅、吹著紫金簫的韓湘子，以及手持荷花的何仙姑。今所見二結王公廟舊廟為1929-1932（昭和4-7）年間重建，2002年經宜蘭縣政府公告登錄為歷史建築。\n\n","Keyword_Rights_2":"CC BY / CC BY / CC BY / CC BY","Keyword_Des_Rights_2":"CC0","Keyword_Longitude":"121.76792","Keyword_Latitude":"24.704695","Original_Url":"https://cmsdb.culture.tw/place/001D1B2E-B62A-4E5D-B38D-943F68BE6E57","Original_Identifier":"512846","Keyword_Subject_1":"民俗與宗教","alias":"","Keywords":"八仙柱 / 凹壽 / 石雕 / 鎮安廟","historicalDates":"","LastUpdateTime":"2020/10/27 19:59:04","timelines":"","place":"","address":"宜蘭縣五結鄉舊街路98號","longitude":"121.76792","latitude":"24.704695","phone":"","Event":"","relationPeople":"","open":"0","free":"否","openTime":"","openTimeDescription":"","capacity":"","traffic":"","subjection":"","tag":"","situation":"","historicalDataBrief":"","historicalData":"","reference":"呈丰建築師事務所（2019），《歷史建築二結王公廟調查研究報告書》。","writer":"林鴻文／蔡明志","createOrgName":"宜蘭縣政府文化局","source":"呈丰建築師事務所（2019），《歷史建築二結王公廟調查研究報告書》。","Keyword_Rights_1":"","AllImages":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-07-22/b6e8a148-a5e6-4d76-82a3-34598e62c3ee/collectionOpen/3f53e152-8db5-4d95-af7b-488b5be12765/109-her-pa-2220-re-202007192230455f1457e39261d0.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-07-22/b6e8a148-a5e6-4d76-82a3-34598e62c3ee/collectionOpen/6ab5446b-d776-47fd-8ca1-6f016ecef726/109-her-pa-2220-re-202007192230455f1457e39261d1.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-07-22/b6e8a148-a5e6-4d76-82a3-34598e62c3ee/collectionOpen/c5411931-bd72-47bb-844e-fbaf1448da5e/109-her-pa-2220-re-202007192230455f1457e39261d2.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-07-22/b6e8a148-a5e6-4d76-82a3-34598e62c3ee/collectionOpen/b2b36079-0598-4c34-ab2e-ef12f3214daf/109-her-pa-2220-re-202007192230455f1457e39261d3.jpg"}}